Conclusions: (link your conclusion from the objective)

- Upon performing this midterm examination i have noticed that all the tasks that we were required to do are already done by us in previous hands on activities, however the implementation of roles is much more difficult as well as new services are being installed such as grafana and influx db which i have encountered a problem in doing so, My playbook runs correctly on those services but upon checking their status the service is not found. Due to the limited time that i have got i have decided not to include grafana in both ubuntu and centos operating system. This hands on activity has challenged me in terms of time management and critical thinking.
